This stores all the logs for when the organizer is running. 
It can be used for debugging and troubleshooting purposes. 
Each entry in the log will typically include a timestamp, the level of the log (e.g., INFO, WARNING, ERROR), 
and a message describing the event or action that occurred. The log canbe helpful for developers to track the flow of 
the application, identify any issues, and understand how theorganizer is performing over time. 